(i) $2 \mathrm{Al}(s)+6 \mathrm{HCl}(a q) \longrightarrow 2 \mathrm{AlCl}_3(a q)+3 \mathrm{H}_2$
(ii)
$$
\begin{aligned}
2 \mathrm{Al}(s)+2 \mathrm{NaOH}(a q) \longrightarrow &amp; \\
&amp; 2 \mathrm{Na}\left[\mathrm{Al}(\mathrm{OH})_4\right]+3 \mathrm{H}_2 \\
&amp; \begin{array}{l}
\text { Sodium tetrahydroxo } \\
\text { aluminate (III) }
\end{array}
\end{aligned}
$$
(iii)
$$
\begin{aligned}
\mathrm{NaBH}_4+\mathrm{I}_2 \longrightarrow &amp; \mathrm{BH}_3+\mathrm{NaI}+\mathrm{HI} \\
&amp; \downarrow\left(\mathrm{NaBH}_4\right) \\
&amp; 2 \mathrm{BH}_3+2 \mathrm{NaI}+\mathrm{H}_2
\end{aligned}
$$
